com.interpss.simu.mnet
Interface AclfBusChildNetRef

All Superinterfaces:
AclfBus, Bus, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAdaptable, IBusChildNetRef, IBusSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AclfBusChildNetRefImpl
public interface AclfBusChildNetRef
extends AclfBus, IBusChildNetRef

A representation of the model object 'Bus Net Ref'. AclfBus class containing a Network object for multi-net algorithm implementation. The bus has to be a PQ bus. The swingBusId defines a bus in the referenced Net object whose voltage and angle are updated.

The following features are supported:

  • Swing Bus Id
  • Child Net Ref

See Also:
MultiNetPackage.getAclfBusChildNetRef()
